<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Edit Book Details</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css"/>
    
    <style>
        body {
            background: #eef2f3;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .main-card {
            border: none;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            max-width: 900px;
            width: 100%;
            background: white;
        }

        /* Left Side (Warning/Info) */
        .info-side {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9966 0%, #ff5e62 100%); /* Orange Gradient for Edit */
            color: white;
            padding: 40px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .info-icon { font-size: 80px; margin-bottom: 20px; animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
        
        /* Right Side (Form) */
        .form-side { padding: 40px; }
        
        .form-floating > .form-control:focus ~ label { color: #ff5e62; font-weight: bold; }
        .form-control:focus { border-color: #ff5e62; box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.25rem rgba(255, 94, 98, 0.25); }

        .btn-update {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff9966, #ff5e62);
            border: none;
            color: white;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-update:hover { transform: scale(1.02); color: white; }
        
        .btn-cancel {
            display: block;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 15px;
            color: #666;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .btn-cancel:hover { color: #333; text-decoration: underline; }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="main-card animate__animated animate__fadeIn">
        <div class="row g-0">
            
            <div class="col-md-5 info-side d-none d-md-flex">
                <div class="info-icon">‚úèÔ∏è</div>
                <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3">Update Details</h2>
                <p class="opacity-75">Mistake ho gayi thi? Koi baat nahi, yahan theek kar lo.</p>
                <div class="mt-4 p-3 bg-white bg-opacity-25 rounded">
                    <small>Tip: Price update karne se customers attract ho sakte hain!</small>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-7 form-side">
                <h3 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-4">Edit Book Information</h3>

                <form action="/update/<%= book.id %>" method="POST">
                    
                    <div class="row g-2 mb-3">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="form-floating">
                                <input type="text" name="name" class="form-control" id="bookName" value="<%= book.name %>" required>
                                <label for="bookName">Book Name</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="form-floating">
                                <input type="text" name="author" class="form-control" id="authorName" value="<%= book.author %>" required>
                                <label for="authorName">Author</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row g-2 mb-4">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="form-floating">
                                <input type="number" name="price" class="form-control" id="price" value="<%= book.price %>" required>
                                <label for="price">Price (‚Çπ)</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="form-floating">
                                <input type="text" name="contact" class="form-control" id="contact" value="<%= book.contact_number %>" required>
                                <label for="contact">Mobile No.</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <button type="submit" class="btn-update w-100 shadow">
                        Save Changes üíæ
                    </button>
                    
                    <a href="/" class="btn-cancel">Cancel & Go Back</a>
                </form>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>